<li id="c284">
  <div class="cx" id="cx50134631">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">Back in the early 90s when I tried to </span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1207970/50134631#c284?mode=alone;showrate=1#c284">2+ / 0-</a>)</span>
